MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2001-0871. State v. Ahmed.

Belmont C.P. No. 99CR192. On motion for ruling on claimed conflict of interest. Motion stricken.

Cook, J., would deny the motion.

On pro se motion to disqualify and remove Public Defender’s Office from representation of appellant and pro se motion for stay of proceedings. Motions denied.
